He stood spell-bound under the witchery of her beauty.
"I came to warn you, Prince," she said, and her soft musical voice set every nerve in Thorndyke's body to tingling with delight.
"My father has banished the faithful slave that you love, but you must not show the anger that you feel, else he will kill you.
