They may do as they will with me if they only will let me see you now and then."
The princess was deeply moved.
The blood rushed to her face and beautified it.
Her eyes fell beneath his admiring glance.
Thorndyke could not restrain himself.
He caught her slender hand and pressed it passionately to his lips, and she made only a slight effort to prevent it.
"I am your obedient slave; what shall I do?"
he asked.
"Do not try to rescue him now," she said softly.
